<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM4.4.3">
<l>aṟiyuñcen tīyait taḻuvi yaccuta ṉeṉṉumey vēvā</l>
<l>ḷeṟiyuntaṇ kāṟṟait taḻuvi yeṉṉuṭaik kōvintaṉ ṉeṉṉum</l>
<l>veṟiko ṭoḻāymalar nāṟum viṉaiyuṭai yāṭṭiyēṉ peṟṟa</l>
<l>ceṟivaḷai muṉkaic ciṟumāṉ ceykiṉṟa teṉkaṇṇuk koṉṟē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Embracing the red fire she knows she says “Acchyuta”, body unburned,</l>
<l>embracing the blowing cool wind she says “my Kōvintaṉ”,</l>
<l>she is fragrant with perfumed Tulsi flowers. [All] one to my eyes [is] what is done</l>
<l>by the little doe with tight bangles on [her] forearms, begotten by me woman with [old] Karma.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
